        public double getOffensiveEfficiency()
        Returns team offensive efficiency value

        Formula: total points / (field goals attempted + free throws attempted)

        Note: Be careful of integer division!

        Returns:
        Offensive Effeciency value

      • getDefensiveEfficiency

        Note: Be careful of integer division!

        Returns:

      • getOverallEfficiency

        public double getOverallEfficiency()
        Returns team overall efficiency value

        Formula: (((offensive efficiency * 2) + (defensive effeciency * 3)) / 5.0) * winning percentage

        Note: Be careful of integer division!

        Returns:
        Defensive Effeciency value
